          "body": "_Part of **Phase 8 — React frontend rebuild**. See `planning/phase-8-react-rebuild.md` (gitignored). Ticket **T23** (resume-boost extra)._\n\nNot blocked by Phase 8 — can ship anytime before or during. Add a `header { ... }` block to the `blog.vics.codes`, `beta.blog.vics.codes`, and `api.blog.vics.codes` Caddy blocks:\n\n- `Content-Security-Policy` — script-src self + inline scripts only where needed (the FOUC prevention snippet); connect-src includes `api.blog.vics.codes`; upgrade-insecure-requests.\n- `Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload` — then submit to hstspreload.org.\n- `X-Frame-Options: DENY` (or `Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'none'`).\n- `Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin`.\n- `X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff`.\n- `Permissions-Policy` — deny camera/mic/geo by default.\n\nVerify with `curl -I` and https://securityheaders.com — target grade A or A+. Talking point: aligns with the DevSecOps target and takes 30 minutes.\n",
